data.description: Introducing a charming residential house with a brick and vinyl exterior, situated on a large lot in a well established neighborhood. This property boasts of a spacious driveway, providing ample parking space for residents and guests alike. Inside, you'll find a thoughtfully designed layout featuring three comfortable bedrooms, two full bathrooms, and bonus room ensuring privacy and convenience for everyone. The large living room offers a welcoming space for relaxation and entertainment, perfect for creating lasting memories with loved ones. Step onto the bamboo flooring that adds a touch of elegance and sustainability to the home. The cathedral ceilings enhance the overall sense of openness and provide an airy atmosphere throughout. A new roof installed in Sept. 2021. With its attractive exterior, spacious interior, and desirable features such as bamboo flooring and cathedral ceilings, this residential house offers a delightful living experience. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home.
